article.headline: Walker's 21 help Robert Morris knock off Detroit Mercy 75-67
article.description: — Stephaun Walker's 21 points helped Robert Morris defeat Detroit Mercy 75-67 on Saturday.
article.linkText: Walker's 21 help Robert Morris knock off Detroit Mercy 75-67
article.story: DETROIT -- — Stephaun Walker's 21 points helped Robert Morris defeat Detroit Mercy 75-67 on Saturday. Walker added seven rebounds for the Colonials (9-14, 5-7 Horizon League). Josh Corbin added 20 points while shooting 6 for 15 (4 for 11 from 3-point range) and 4 of 5 from the free throw line, and he also had 11 rebounds. Markeese Hastings was 4 of 8 shooting (0 for 3 from 3-point range) to finish with 10 points. Jayden Stone led the way for the Titans (0-24, 0-13) with 25 points and six rebounds. Marcus Tankersley added 24 points for Detroit Mercy. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
